des:
Produced by Frank Kilpatrick in collaboration with Grammy Award-winning Producer Alex Wand, and bilingual composer and performer Rayko, the Gratitude music/video series provides either energizing or relaxing auditory experiences by employing microtonal arrangements, enchanting visuals and affirming messages.
